            <div class="card about-section">
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>Welcome to **Blossom Bites Canteen**, your trusted partner in managing canteen services with a
                        modern touch. Our Canteen Management System was born out of a simple idea: to make campus and
                        workplace dining more efficient, transparent, and enjoyable for everyone. We saw the long
                        queues, the manual order-taking, and the lack of real-time information, and we knew there was a
                        better way.</p>
                    <p>Our team is passionate about using technology to solve everyday problems. We've built a system
                        that streamlines every aspect of canteen operations, from food ordering and payment to inventory
                        management and data analytics. Our goal is to create a seamless experience for both the
                        students/employees and the canteen staff.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

